{"tid":858482,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"第三天了，大陸教師依然放生保皇狗","createTime":"2018-10-12T00:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T05:10:40.000Z","uid":38523,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf969057d9c7162327c42fa35cc3c88ab40cdfcf","tid":858482,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:10:47.000Z","msg":"樣樣都做<br />\n唯獨保皇狗就放生<br />\n我保証<br />\n到補選前<br />\n呢位大陸教師又會做下樣<br />\n叫人投白票<br />\n幫保皇狗勝率由99%提升至百分百<br />\n睇下佢出幾多力屌保皇狗？<br />\n人地屌保皇狗佢就入來用保皇狗以外既政黨轉移視線<br />\n一個雨革完即刻去大陸做四年既人<br />\n你信？<br />\n因為佢知<br />\n只要保皇狗在就冇問題<br />\n佢搞其他野只係為左係關鍵時候可以幫保皇狗排除對手"},{"pid":"a5b79035c14218086bf7d0d0d6ebc43454f6dacf","tid":858482,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8718c0e589e51bd4f13e0ee28b3d6585288edb","tid":858482,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6deba10b95b93d968a4a07340fe294a43061682c","tid":858482,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b9072693ab0614d8b9f5946fdf2b295a8ac063","tid":858482,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:54:44.000Z","msg":"負評來講<br />\n關狗都好落力<br />\n如果可以分小小去屌保皇狗就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/he